snippet.title: Loopmancer - Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the latest trailer for Loopmancer, a 3D platforming roguelite action game, all packed in a cyberpunk universe. Loopmancer will be available on 13th July 2022, on Epic Games Store and Steam.

#Loopmancer
